<bibRefCitation id="8764569B475CFFDAC584E300FC9DFBE7" author="Omid" box="[644,840,1052,1077]" pageId="13" pageNumber="414" refString="Omid, R., Azizkhani, E., Yarmand, H., Neinavai, F. &amp; Lindelow, A. (2011) Report of two bark beetles species of the family Scolytidae in imported wood from Russia. Iranian Journal of Forest and Range Protection Research, 9, 80 - 81." type="journal article" year="2011">
